      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ARVADA (2) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (22.32) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 390m. Got the money at her only try from this box. Rates highly and will give a great sight. QUEST FOR STYLE (4) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 1.75 lengths (22.10) at this track. Harder here but expected to feature again. SLICK TOMMY (6) is a talented type who notched his 14th career success when too good (22.16) at this track last time. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can make it back-to-back wins. SKETCHY DEMOS (1) was below best last time at Warrnambool (26.24) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 10 length eighth. Has seven wins already from this draw.",
